{
  "stem": "5228.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was standing like this while I was naked, and he come with a stick and beat me up on the back, the SS there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then I was standing already straight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I couldn't stand straight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, it was terrible, the-- the back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then they gave us-- for everybody-- a black dress.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they put such a yellow stripes on it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "From the back, if we run away, then nobody would-- then we cannot run, and they will recognize us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They didn't give nothing, underwear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Nothing, just the one-- a dress.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So that's-- that's how we was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That's finished already.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that's how we was in-- in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That means-- that was what they will kill us all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's why they didn't give numbers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The girls what they took right away to work, and when they took us to work, when I was going to work, when they took us to Boizenburg there in the factory, in the the airplane factory, they didn't give more the numbers.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
